        </figure>
        <list id="id12795836" list-type="bulleted">
          <item>You require 150 N to crack the nut.</item>
        </list>
        <para id="id12782787">a) Which FORCE is needed?</para>
        <para id="id12544499"/>
        <para id="id5715450"/>
        <para id="id12866262">b) What is the mechanical advantage of the nutcracker?</para>
